quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  47,20,"Ba-kholoang ba re: “Hobaneng Khaolo e sa romeloe ho rona? Empa ha Khaolo e totobetseng, e bolela ka ntoa, u tla bona bao lipelong ho bona ho tletseng maloetse ba u shalimile joalo ka ha eka ba makhatheng a lefu. Empa ba ne ba loketse"
  47,21,"Ho amohela ba bue toka, hore ha taba e rarolotsoe, e ne etla ba molemo ha ba ne ba ena le ‘nete ho Allah"
  47,22,"Joale, ho lebeletsoe ho tsoa ho uena haeba u fuoe matla, hore u tla fehla mofere-fere holim’a lefats’e, u khaole maqhama a tsoalano le beng ka uena"
  47,23,Ba joalo ke batho bao Allah A ba rohakileng hobane U ba entse Litholo le ho ba foufatsa
  47,24,"Joale ha ba leke ka matla ho batla ho utloisisa Qura’n, kapa lipelo tsa bona ba li tlamme mafito"
  47,25,"Haele ba koenehang kamor’a hoba tataiso e totobatsoe kapel’a bona, E Mobe o ba ekile; ka ts’episo ea mafeela"
  47,26,"Sena ke hobane ba re ho ba hloileng molaetsa o senotsoeng ke Allah: “Re tla le mamela karolong ea litaba tsena;” empa Allah U tseba liphiri tsa bona"
  47,27,"Empa ho tlaba joang mohla manyeloi a nkang meea ea bona lefung, a ba otla lifahlehong le ka mekokotlong"
  47,28,"Sena e le hobane ba ile ba latela se khopisang Allah, eaba ba hloea se Mo thabisang. Kahoo, o fetotse liketso tsa bona mafeela"
  47,29,Kapa bao Lipelo tsa bona li tletseng maloetse ba nahana hore Allah A ke ke A behaa pooaneng lehloeo la bona